\f0\fs26 \cf0 Welcome to the Biblical Hebew Keyboards Installer v1.1.\
\
These keyboards have been designed to assist in typing text for Biblical Hebrew.  Unlike keyboards for modern Hebrew, they have been desiged for easy access for diacritical marks, including vowels and cantilation marks.  They may be used with any Unicode-compatible fonts that contain the Hebrew character set, but they are designed espicially for use with SBL Hebrew.   \
\
This will program will install the 2 Biblical Hebrew keyboards, one based on the SIL layout, and the other based on the Tiro layout.  \
\
Documentation for the keyboards, as well as the SBL Hebrew font, may be found at the SBL website, www.sbl-site.org.}]]></welcome>
